    <item>
      <title>Virtual Learning Sessions</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/50464431327665/huge/d14c573a3bf4b0f3b4419e69ebe495cd898be714.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Wed, 11 Mar 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>We’re excited to announce the launch of HU Learning Hours, a new professional development initiative designed to meet the evolving needs of our campus community. Whether you’re looking to sharpen your skills, connect with colleagues, or lead with greater impact, HU Learning Hours offers multiple ways to learn, grow, and connect.</p>

<p> </p>

<p>🖥️ Virtual Learning Sessions (2nd Wednesdays)</p>

<p> University-Wide Session: 10 a.m. People Leader Session: 1 p.m. </p>

<p>Take your learning further with these hands-on, 60-90 minute sessions where you can practice, collaborate, and build confidence in a supportive environment. Check out the HU Learning Hours website and register for your sessions today.</p>

<p><a href="https://events.howard.edu/event/virtual-learning-sessions">View on site</a> | <a href="mailto:?subject=I found an interesting event%3A Virtual Learning Sessions&amp;body=I found an interesting event you may like%3A%0A%0A%0ADate%3A Mar 11%2C 2026%0A%0ADescription%3A%0AWe%E2%80%99re excited to announce the launch of HU Learning Hours%2C a new professional development initiative designed to meet the evolving needs of our campus community. Whether you%E2%80%99re looking to sharpen your skills%2C connect with colleagues%2C or lead with greater impact%2C HU Learning Hours offers multiple ways to learn%2C grow%2C and connect.%0A%0A %0A%0A%F0%9F%96%A5%EF%B8%8F Virtual Learning Sessions %282nd Wednesdays%29%0A%0A University-Wide Session%3A 10 a.m. People Leader Session%3A 1 p.m. %0A%0ATake your learning further with these hands-on%2C 60-90 minute sessions where you can practice%2C collaborate%2C and build confidence in a supportive environment. Check out the HU Learning Hours website and register for your sessions today.%0A%0Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fevents.howard.edu%2Fevent%2Fvirtual-learning-sessions%0A">Email this event</a></p></div></div>]]></description>
